@node Main "Hexarrow - Documentation"

                             'Hexarrow' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Hexarrow' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} that is played on an hexagonal
shaped game board that is full of arrows that are pointing in
various directions. The idea is to move all those arrows toward an
exit tile, represented by an hexagonal 'hole'.

  To move, an arrow must point toward an empty space (or the exit
tile). Otherwise, it will turn clockwise by 60 degrees...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

