@node features "Features"

                               Features

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Hexarrow is a "Workbench" game, so it is meant to be played on
 the Workbench screen. The game window can be resized to the
 desired size. If the window is too small, click inside the window
 and Hexarrow will resize its window to an adequate size.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Hexarrow works on all 68020(+) Amigas with Workbench 2.0 or
 higher.

